{
    "attributes": {
        "action": "Ban MPs from having second jobs except in NHS",
        "additional_details": "Parliament should ban any sitting MPs from having second jobs as we feel it is a conflict of interest.\r\n \r\nThe only exception to this rule are if the MPs are qualified doctors, nurses or other healthcare professionals who actively work within the NHS.",
        "background": "MPs should not have other jobs outside of Parliament unless they are qualified doctors, nurses or other healthcare professionals and actively work in the NHS",
